'''Vondar Canyon''' was a canyon on [[Aargonar/Legends|Aargonar]]. During the [[Battle of Aargonar (Clone Wars)|Battle of Aargonar]], it was used as a staging area by [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] under the command of [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Ki-Adi-Mundi/Legends|Ki-Adi-Mundi]].

